{
  "day": "1",
  "heading": "Reach Pokhara from Kathmandu",
  "sub_heading": "Drive distance: 215 km | Trek Duration: 7 hours | Stay for Indiahikes Trekkers: Pokhara Top and Top Hotel, Pokhara",
  "details": "You will reach Pokhara on your own by either taking a bus or flying in from Kathmandu. You are expected to reach by 4 pm. You will meet the rest of the team at Pokhara Top and Top Hotel. Your stay at Pokhara Top and Top Hotel is taken care of by Indiahikes. You don't need to pay extra for this.\nPlease note: We will only be serving dinner at Hotel Pokhara Top and Top after trekkers arrive post 4 pm."
}

{
  "day": "2",
  "heading": "Drive from Pokhara to Kimsee. Trek to Ghandruk",
  "sub_heading": "Drive Distance: 56 km | Trek Duration: 2.5 hours | Altitude Gain: 2,760 ft to 5,440 ft\nTrek Distance: 3.7 km | Trek Duration: 2 hours | Altitude Gain: 5,440 ft to 6,561 ft",
  "details": "Transport will be arranged by Indiahikes, but the trekkers will have to share the cost. Approx Rs 2,500 INR per person including both the drives to the base camp."
}

